It hits the sweet spot of sound, design, and features for Andrew:
Tuned with full, controlled bass and smooth mids, so reggae basslines and R&B vocals feel rich without * getting muddy.
Class‑leading noise canceling and very comfortable, lightweight build for long listening sessions.
Extremely clean, minimal styling in black or neutral finishes that aligns well with a chic, understated aesthetic.
Industry-leading ANC technology that adapts to your environment in real-time
Up to 30 hours of continuous playback on a single charge
High-resolution audio with dual noise-sensing microphones for pristine clarity
Lightweight, premium materials with memory foam ear pads for all-day wear
Multipoint Bluetooth 5.3 connectivity to switch seamlessly between two devices
3-minute charge provides up to 3 hours of playback time
Strong feature set: multipoint Bluetooth, good app, and support for high‑res wireless codecs.
Industry‑leading active noise cancellation that blocks airplane engines, traffic, and office noise extremely well.​
Comfortable, lightweight over‑ear design that most people can wear for long listening or travel sessions.
Plasticky build and hinge durability concerns feel underwhelming for the price.
Stock sound can be mediocre or muddy without EQ, with limited soundstage and detail versus some competitors.
Comfort can be mixed for larger heads; the thinner headband may create pressure over long sessions.
